    "display_name": "School Administrator",
    "long_instructions": "## Dr. James Patel, School Administrator\r\n\r\n**Location:** Toronto, Canada\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Maplewood Public Schools\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Educational technology, curriculum development, school leadership\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"SMART Boards help us modernize classrooms by integrating digital learning. We ensure teachers are trained to use these tools effectively, making education more dynamic and collaborative for students.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
